## Architectural Decisions Log

| Decision | Date | Reason |
|----------|------|--------|
| LangChain RAG replaces pattern-matching AI | Mar 2026 | 4,649 → 481 lines; semantic search; self-learning |
| `gpt-4o-mini` for all non-KYC OpenAI calls | Mar 2026 | Cost: ~$30k/month → ~$150-360/month at 3M users |
| KYC stays on `gpt-4o` | Mar 2026 | POPIA accuracy requirement |
| Figma restriction removed | Feb 2026 | Code is source of truth; agents edit `.tsx` freely |
| Agent commits AND pushes to main | Feb 2026 | Streamlined workflow |
| Cloud Build for deployments (not local Docker) | Mar 2026 | No Docker Desktop needed; faster build times |
| MT940+MT942 for SBSA H2H statements | Mar 2026 | SWIFT ISO standard — banking/Mojaloop grade |
| Sub-folders in GCS for SBSA files | Mar 2026 | statements/ and payments/ separation prevents file mixing |
| Admin user for all DDL migrations | Mar 2026 | mymoolah_app is DML only; postgres superuser required for ALTER/CREATE |
| USSD eeziCash fixed to use Wallet.debit() + SELECT FOR UPDATE | Mar 2026 | Previous impl bypassed double-entry ledger with direct SQL; now uses Wallet model with row-level locking |
| In-memory supplier circuit breaker (not Redis) | Mar 2026 | Acceptable for single-instance; migrate to Redis for horizontal scaling on Cloud Run |
| Supplier failover via composite key matching (not product names) | Mar 2026 | Product names inconsistent across suppliers; deterministic keys (vasType+provider+priceType/amount) used instead |
| Overlay route still has inline MobileMart failover alongside new CB | Mar 2026 | Old SupplierComparisonService failover in overlayServices.js coexists with new circuit breaker pre-check; consolidate in future refactor |
| MM_DEPLOYMENT_ENV baked into deploy scripts | Mar 2026 | Cloud Run `--set-env-vars` replaces ALL env vars; manually-set vars lost on redeploy. Now permanent in staging + production scripts |
| Real PNG brand assets for network logos | Mar 2026 | Hand-drawn SVG cannot accurately reproduce brand marks; import PNGs as Vite modules from `assets/` |
| Voucher overlay uses productPurchaseService (not inline route) | Mar 2026 | Banking-grade architecture: service layer handles ACID transactions, idempotency, circuit breaker, commission. Overlay route is thin catalog query only. Other overlays should follow this pattern (flagged as tech debt). |
| Cloud Scheduler replaces node-cron for catalog sync | Apr 2026 | Cloud Run kills idle instances mid-sweep (~16 min in). Cloud Scheduler sends HTTP POST that keeps instance alive. OIDC auth, 1800s timeout, 3 retries. Node-cron kept as fallback for local dev. |
| SBSA statement poller: .keep file filter + GCS permissions fixed | Mar 2026 | Poller accepted all files (including .keep placeholder) — now only accepts FINSTMT/PROVSTMT patterns. Both staging+production SAs granted objectAdmin on sftp-inbound bucket. |
| RTP CdtrRefInf.Ref uses creditor MSISDN from DB (not user input) | Apr 2026 | User-provided description in remittance info would break deposit notification service wallet auto-matching. Phone sourced from `users.phoneNumber`, converted to local `0`-prefixed format. User description preserved in metadata as `userDescription`. |
| v_best_offers materialized view replaces 6 files + 3 tables | Apr 2026 | 8+ tables/6 services/3,400+ lines replaced by one SQL view + one service. Selection rules in DB table (`product_selection_rules`). Commission config externalized to JSON. Staging validated; production pending. |
| Commission config externalized to JSON | Apr 2026 | 150 lines of hardcoded if/else commission maps replaced by `config/supplier-commissions.json`. Config changes no longer require code changes. |

## Rule: When to Add Here

Add an entry whenever you:
- Identify code complexity or duplication that should be refactored
- Make an architectural decision that future agents should understand
- Find a bug you can't fix in the current session
- Notice a pattern that differs from the project standards
